import random
secretNumber = random.randint(1,20)
numberGuesses = random.randint(5,10)
print("I am thinking of a number between 1 and 20")
print("You have", numberGuesses, "guesses")
print(" ")

for numberGuesses in range(random.randint(5,10)):
    prompt="Guess #"+ str(numberGuesses)
    guess=int(input(prompt))
    if(guess == secretNumber):
        print("Yes!")
        break
    
    elif(guess>secretNumber):
        print(guess, "is too high")
    elif(guess<secretNumber):
        print(guess, "is too low")
    else:
        print("No, my number is not", guess)
            
print("The secret number was", secretNumber)
